==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncanonize
<hw>Un*can"on*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>canonize</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To deprive
of canonical authority.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To reduce from the rank of a canonized
saint.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncap</ent>⟦br⟧
